msgid "Module for managing calendar events and schedules."
msgstr "Module de gestion des evenements de calendrier et des plannings."

msgid ""
"Restored CSRF protection on SaveCalendarPreferencesView (removed "
"@csrf_exempt). Migrated signal and timezone imports to the horilla shims and "
"standardized first-party import groups; behavior unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Protection CSRF restauree sur SaveCalendarPreferencesView. Migration des "
"imports de signaux et de fuseaux horaires vers les shims horilla ; "
"comportement inchange."

msgid ""
"Custom calendar form aligned with HorillaModelForm layout: field_order, Meta."
"fields = \"__all__\", and Meta.exclude; save logic and HTMX behavior "
"unchanged."
msgstr ""
"Formulaire de calendrier personnalise aligne sur le layout HorillaModelForm : "
"field_order, Meta.fields et Meta.exclude ; logique de sauvegarde et HTMX "
"inchanges."

msgid ""
"Google Calendar integration settings now pass the full request on POST so "
"get_or_create uses the active company consistently with GET."
msgstr ""
"Les parametres d'integration Google Calendar transmettent maintenant la "
"requete complete sur POST afin que get_or_create utilise la societe active "
"de facon coherente avec GET."

msgid ""
"Release 1.10: calendar ships under contrib with app label calendar. Google "
"Calendar sync, webhook settings, namespaces, templates, and integrations "
"updated from the legacy calendar app naming."
msgstr ""
"Version 1.10 : le calendrier est integre sous contrib avec le label "
"d'application calendar. La synchronisation Google Calendar, les parametres "
"webhook, les espaces de noms, les modeles et les integrations ont ete mis a jour."

msgid ""
"Introduced Google Calendar integration with sync capabilities, service "
"configuration, and settings management for seamless external calendar "
"connectivity."
msgstr ""
"Introduction de l'integration Google Calendar avec des capacites de "
"synchronisation, la configuration du service et la gestion des parametres "
"pour une connectivite externe fluide."

msgid ""
"Compatibility updates and minor internal improvements to align with platform "
"architecture and generics framework updates."
msgstr ""
"Mises a jour de compatibilite et ameliorations internes mineures pour "
"s'aligner sur l'architecture de la plateforme et les mises a jour du "
"framework generics."

msgid ""
"Migrated from Django AppConfig to Horilla AppLauncher and replaced Django "
"utilities with horilla.utils.decorators, horilla.utils.translation, and "
"horilla.shortcuts where applicable."
msgstr ""
"Migration de Django AppConfig vers Horilla AppLauncher et remplacement des "
"utilitaires Django par horilla.utils.decorators, horilla.utils.translation "
"et horilla.shortcuts selon le cas."

